SENATE BILL NO. 1753
103RD GENERAL ASSEMBLY
INTRODUCED BY SENATOR HOUGH.
7432S.01I KRISTINA MARTIN, Secretary
AN ACT
1
2 To appropriate money for the expenses, grants, refunds, and distributions of the Department
3 of Revenue, the Department of Transportation, and the several divisions and
4 programs thereof, to be expended only as provided in Article IV, Section 28 of the
5 Constitution of Missouri, and to transfer money among certain funds for the period
6 beginning July 1, 2026, and ending June 30, 2027.
7
8 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the state of Missouri, as follows:
9
